      • stepM

        public Bit stepM()
        Mutable simulate Step operation of LSFRs. XORs the taps, pushes the result from the left, and shifts the contents to the right and returns the right-most bit that shifted off as the output.
        Returns:
        the output of the Step operation

        Simulate Step operation of LSFRs. XORs the taps, pushes the result from the left, and shifts the contents to the right and returns the right-most bit that shifted off as the output.
